<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَيَجُوزُ الِاقْتِصَارُ عَلَى وَاحِدٍ مِنْ صِنْفٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- وَتُسَنُّ إِلَى مَنْ لَا تَلْزَمُهُ مُؤْنَتُهُ مِنْ أَقَارَبِهِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَمَنْ أُبِيحَ لَهُ أَخْذُ شَيْءٍ أُبِيحَ لَهُ سُؤَالُهُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- وَيَجِبُ قَبُولُ مَالٍ طَيِّبٍ أَتَى بِلَا مَسْأَلَةٍ وَلَا اسْتِشَرَافِ نَفْسٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَإِنْ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- تَفَرَّغَ قَادِرٌ عَلَى التَّكَسُّبِ لِلعِلْمِ الشَّرْعِيِّ لَا لِلعِبَادَةِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَتَعَذَّرَ الجَمْعُ بَيْنِ التَّكَسُّبِ وَالِاشْتِغَالِ بِالعِلْمِ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>أُعْطِيَ مِنْ زَكَاةٍ لِحَاجَتِهِ؛ وَإِنْ لَمْ يَكُنِ العِلْمُ لَازِمًا لَهُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَلَا يُجْزِئُ دَفْعُهَا:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> إِلَى كَافِرٍ غَيْرِ مُؤَلَّفٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَلَا إِلَى كَامِلِ رِقٍّ غَيْرِ:<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- عَامِلٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- وَمُكَاتَبٍ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> وَلَا إِلَى فَقِيرٍ وَمِسْكِينٍ مُسْتَغْنِيَيْنِ بِنَفَقَةٍ وَاجِبَةٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>